*{{cite web|last1=Lilly|first1=Paul|title=This is what your internet service could look like without Net Neutrality|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/this-is-what-your-internet-service-could-look-like-without-net-neutrality/|website=[[PC Gamer]]|language=en|date=31 October 2017}}
*{{cite web|author1=The Logical Indian Crew|title=What Would The Internet Be Like Without Net Neutrality? Portugal Is An Example|url=https://thelogicalindian.com/awareness/net-neutrality-portugal/|website=The Logical Indian|date=1 November 2017}}
*{{cite web|last1=Pelaez|first1=Marina Watson|title=Portugal: Glimpse Into the World Without Net Neutrality|url=http://www.theglobepost.com/2017/11/18/net-neutrality-portugal/|website=The Globe Post|language=en|date=18 November 2017}}
